text: Department of the Treasury Internal Revenue Service
This obsoletes IRM 4.4.29, Audit Information Management System (AIMS) Procedures and Instructions, Social Security Administration (SSA) Adjustments.
The material in this IRM is not part of the validity and consistency of AIMS and is being obsoleted.

IRM Sections Description of Change IRM 4.4.29.1 Previous information for Introduction not needed. Related sections were removed. IRM 4.4.29.2 Previous information for Self-Employment Income Adjustments can be found in IRM 4.23.10.17 and IRM 4.23.10.17.4. IRM 4.4.29.2.1 Previous procedures for Group Return Process- ing Procedures can be found in IRM 4.23.10.17.1(5), IRM 4.23.10.2, IRM 4.23.10.20, and IRM 4.4.29.5. IRM 4.4.29.2.1.1 Previous information for Reference Code Changes to Self-employment Income/Tax can be found in IRM 4.10.8.18.8 and IRM 4.23.10.17.1. IRM 4.4.29.3 Previous procedures for Group Procedures for Adjustments to Tip Income not needed. Related sections have been removed. IRM 4.4.29.3.1 and IRM 4.4.39.3.1(a) Previous information for Group Procedures can be found in IRM 4.23.10.18 and IRM 4.23.7.4. IRM 4.4.29.3.1 (b) The form mentioned in Group Procedures has been made obsolete by the Small Business/ Self-Employed (SB/SE) Functional Liaison Coordinator. This item was deemed obsolete during a 508 compliance review by Publishing. Current procedures can be found in IRM 4.23.7.4. IRM 4.4.29.3.2 Previous information for Reference Code Changes to Tip Income can be found in IRM 4.23.10.18.

IRM Sections Description of Change IRM 4.4.29.3.3 The form discussed in CCP Procedures for Reviewing Form 885-T is obsolete as of 03/29/ 2019. New procedures can be found in IRM Exhibit 4.23.7-3. IRM 4.4.29.4 Previous information for Group Procedures for FICA Tax Adjustments can be found in IRM 4.10.8.14.10, IRM 4.23.7.7.3, IRM 4.23.10.16.1, IRM 4.23.10.17, and IRM 4.23.10.17.2. IRM 4.4.29.5 Previous information for Group Procedures for FICA or Railroad Retirement Tax Adjustments Due to Tip Income can be found in IRM 4.23.7.2, IRM 4.23.7.3.1, IRM 4.23.7.7.3, IRM 4.23.10.10.1, and IRM 4.23.10.17.1.
Large Business & International (LB&I), Wage and Investment (W&I), and Small Business/Self-Employed (SB/ SE) employees.
